  "PinObjectiveTip": {
    "English": "Craft <span class=\"name name-commodity\">Salt Refractors</span> from <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">Salt</span>. Use <span class=\"name name-img\">PRODMENU</span> to craft in empty <span class=\"name name-technology\">Inventory Slots</span>.<br><span class=\"name name-tradeable\">Salt</span> is readily extracted from <span class=\"name name-earth\">underwater rock deposits</span>. Increase marine efficiency by upgrading the Exosuit <span class=\"name name-technology\">Aeration Membrane</span> or by refilling oxygen supplies from <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">Kelp Sacs</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "使用<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">盐</span>制作<span class=\"name name-commodity\">盐折射器</span>。使用<span class=\"name name-img\">PRODMENU</span>在空置<span class=\"name name-technology\">栏位</span>中制作。<br>从<span class=\"name name-earth\">地下岩石矿床</span>中容易提取出<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">盐</span>。升级套装<span class=\"name name-technology\">换气薄膜</span>或从<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">海藻袋</span>中补充氧气补给，以提高在海洋中的效率。",
    "TencentChinese": "使用<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">盐</span>制作<span class=\"name name-commodity\">盐折射器</span>。使用<span class=\"name name-img\">PRODMENU</span>在空置<span class=\"name name-technology\">栏位</span>中制作。<br>从<span class=\"name name-earth\">地下岩石矿床</span>中容易提取出<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">盐</span>。升级套装<span class=\"name name-technology\">换气薄膜</span>或从<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">海藻袋</span>中补充氧气补给，以提高在海洋中的效率。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "使用<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">鹽</span>製作<span class=\"name name-commodity\">鹽折射體</span>。使用<span class=\"name name-img\">PRODMENU</span>在空置<span class=\"name name-technology\">欄位</span>中製作。<br>從<span class=\"name name-earth\">地下岩石礦床</span>中容易提取出<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">鹽</span>。升級強化套裝<span class=\"name name-technology\">曝氣黏膜</span>或從<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">巨藻囊</span>中補充氧氣補給，以提高在海洋中的效率。"
